  和平: Toa7-gong7 peh, bo5 iau3-kin2, goan2 long2 bo5 teh khioh-hun7 lin2, in-ui7 Ia5-sou kong2: Tioh8 thiaN3 li2 e5 chhu3-piN, chhin-chhiuN7 ka-ki7, goan2 an2-ni choe3 si7 eng3-kai e5. 
