  大憨伯: Na7 si7 goa2 chiah nih8 thou2-phiah m7 chai chaiN2-iuN7 chiah oe7 kai2. 
  溫柔: HouN3! li2 na7 ai3 koe2 seng3-te7 tioh8 lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou pai3 Siong7-te3, Ia5-sou oe7 ka7 lang5 teng5-thau5-siN, oaN7 lang5 e5 phin2-heng7 ke2 lang5 e5 ku7-seng3. 
  大憨伯: Ah! pai3 Siong7-te3 goa2 chin ku2 tioh8 teh siuN7, na7-si7 an2-ni goa2 chit le2-pai3 beh kap lin2 lai5 khi3 le2-pai3. 
  博愛: Chin-ho2! chin-ho2! Toa7-gong7 peh, li2 na7 lai5 sin3 Ia5-sou chiu7 oe7 ho2 seng3-te7, ia7 boe7 koh tui3 keh-piah pun5 teng-he2. 
  善良: A-peh! si7 lah! chit le2-pai3 tek-khak tioh8 lai5, m7 na7 li2 lai5 le2-pai3, Thian-hok kun soa3 hou7 i kap goan2 lai5 khi3 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, au7-lai5 i oe7 ke chin chhong-beng5 koh gau5 iu2-hau3 a-kong. 
