  郵差: Koa3-ho7! chhiaN2 theh8 in3-a2 lai5 tng3. (蓋印) 
  溫柔: Sim2-mih8 lang5 kia3-lai5 e5? 
  和平: Ti7 Bi2-kok goan2 a-hiaN kia3 lai5 e5 (和平讀音信) 
  “A-pa kap sio2-ti7 lin2 u7 peng5-an bo5? Goa2 chu7 li7-khui kau3 chit si5 long2 peng5-an. Goa2 saN-ni5 cheng5 tui3 Hiong-kang2 lai5 Bi2-kok, hian7-chai7 keng-eng5 kang-chhiuN2, bo5 eng5 thang tng2-khi3 lan2 kok, tai7-khai3 me5-ni5 Seng3-tan3 cheh e5 si5-chun7 oe7 tng2-khi3, goa2 chu7 chhut-kok kau3 hian7-chai7 long2 bo5 kia3-chiN5 tng2 khi3, chhiaN2 goan5-liong7. TaN kia3 Bi2-kim 5 ban7-khou chhiaN2 tui3 Hoa5-lam5 gin5-hang5 nia2, na7 eng7-liau2 sia2-phoe lai5, goa2 oe7 koh kia3 khi3, goan7 ThiN-pe7 kap lin2 ti7-teh, peng5-an.” A-pa chit tiuN si7 5 ban7 khou e5 gin5-hang5 toaN.
  大憨伯: Un-jiu5 hiaN kiong-hi2, kiong-hi2, Siong7-te3 u7 iaN2 teh po2-pi3 lin2. (鐘聲) 
  博愛: Ah! cheng-siaN koh teh tan5 lah, chiok-ho7 hoe7 teh beh soah lah. 
  善良: Ah! bo5, lan2 lai5 tiam3 chia chhiuN3 chiok Seng3-tan3 e5 chiok-ho7 koa. 
  (Seng3-tan3 cheng) S.S. Seng3-si te7 4 siu2. (幕) 
  (Oah8-mia7 e5 bi2-niu5 te7 43 ki5, 1957 ni5 12 goeh8) 
